David Schramm (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_Schramm_(actor) 0 David Schramm (born August 14, 1946) is an American actor. He is best known for playing the critically acclaimed role of Roy Biggins, the portly, curmudgeonly rival airline owner in the TV series Wings.
